ACT:
 Constitution of India, Arts. 14 and 16-Discrimination in the matter of conferment of benefit through an administrative order-Letter of President dated November 17, 1953 classifying checkers post in Government Harness and Saddlery Factory, Kanpur as posts of lower division clerks-Appellants denied the designation as clerks while others similarly situate were given the benefit Held discriminatory.
 
